MPX Is in Talks to Buy Power Plants From Bertin, Estado Says

-- B y   L u c i a   K a s s a i
-- 
2011-02-23T13:13:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-23/mpx-is-in-talks-to-buy-power-plants-from-bertin-estado-says.html
  MPX Energia SA  is in talks to buy
thermoelectric  power plants  from Grupo Bertin, Sao Paulo-based
newspaper  O Estado de S. Paulo  reported, without saying where it
got the information.  A spokesman for MPX, who can’t be named because of company
policy, declined to comment in an e-mailed response. Spokesmen
for Bertin didn’t return an e-mail from Bloomberg News seeking
comment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lucia Kassai in  Sao Paulo  at 
 lkassai@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dale Crofts at   dcrofts@bloomberg.net . 